@startuml sequence_update_status
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence — Update Application Status

actor "Job Seeker" as User
participant "data/pipeline.md" as Pipeline
participant "templates/states.yml" as States

User -> Pipeline : Locate row by Company/Role
Pipeline --> User : Returns current row

User -> States : Verify new status value\nis in valid list
States --> User : Confirmed valid

User -> Pipeline : Update Status cell\n(e.g. Applied -> Responded)
User -> Pipeline : Append notes\n(e.g. recruiter name, date)
Pipeline --> User : Row updated

User -> Pipeline : Commit to Git

@enduml
